text: Kim Bong-hyeon (born 11 May 1975) is a South Korean gymnast. He competed in seven events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of South Korea Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
